character.name:
goku He can transform into various Super Saiyan forms, each dramatically increasing his power
His signature attacks include the Kamehameha wave and Spirit Bomb
He's trained under Master Roshi, King Kai, and Whis among others
He's died and been resurrected multiple times throughout the series
His rival/friend Vegeta is one of the most important relationships in the seriesHe inherits the Attack Titan and Founding Titan powers
His character undergoes one of the most dramatic transformations in anime - from an idealistic hero to a morally ambiguous figure
His catchphrase about freedom and destroying his enemies becomes increasingly dark as the story progresses
The final arc reveals his extreme plan to protect Paradis Island, which divides fans on whether he's a hero, villain, or tragic figure
His relationships with Mikasa and Armin are central to the storyHis signature catchphrases: "D'oh!", "Mmm... [food item]", and "Why you little...!" (while strangling Bart)
He loves Duff beer, donuts, and watching TV
Despite his stupidity and selfishness, he genuinely loves his family and often has heartfelt moments
He's caused countless disasters in Springfield through his negligence and poor decisions
His low intelligence is legendary - his brain has even been shown literally shrinking away from vegetables
